(59, 'Termag Hotel – authentic and modern', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Termag Hotel Jahorina is a modern four-star hotel offering a wide range of events and activities all year round. The hotel is located in the centre of the Jahorina Mountain Olympic Ski Centre, next to ski slopes and ski lift, at an altitude of 1550m above sea level. Termag Hotel offers 18 comfortable rooms and 13 suites equipped with modern comforts such as mini bar, satellite TV and Internet. All hotel premises are air-conditioned. Each room also has an underground parking place reserved for the occupant guest. The hotel restaurant offers local and international cuisine specialities and a wide selection of wines and can host up to 120 persons. For a more complete and unique mountain experience, enjoy the Kamin hall (sala) and the ethnic restaurant Koliba, which are part of the Hotel complex. Professional staff in the children&rsquo;s playroom is also at your disposal ensuring safety and entertainment for your children during your stay.<br /><br />We offer a wide selection of Hotel services, including swimming pool, sauna, steam bath, Jacuzzi, fitness centre, solarium and SPA&amp;Wellness Centre. In addition, you can rent or buy skiing equipment or sign up for skiing lessons in our Hotel.<br /><br />In close proximity of the Hotel, next to the ski slope, Koliba Restaurant is situated offering delicious meals during the day and excellent entertainment in the evening.<br /><br />Amir Vuk, the architect from Sarajevo who designed the Hotel, is renowned for his work on the Hotel interior and exterior. One of the most prominent architects in the region, Mr. Vuk chose old worn out wood as the basis, and together with traditional carpenters from Tesanj, brought the Hotel to life.<br /><br />Using natural materials in natural Jahorina Mountain surroundings resulted in the creation of a warm and cozy atmosphere in the entire Hotel. You will meet traditional hospitality and top-rate professionalism at every step of your stay in our Hotel. Our goal, above all, is to provide our guests with a comfortable, home-like ambience, along with a warm and cozy atmosphere! <br /><br /><a href="virtual_tour_dodatno/Hotel"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual tour &gt;</span></a><br /><br /> <a class="link_crveni" href="galerija/hotel">Take a tour of our Photo Gallery&gt;</a></p>', 'o_nama_gore.jpg', 'o_nama_lijevo.jpg', 'About Termag Hotel ', 'Termag', 'o_hotelu', 1, 'en', '', '', ''),
(60, 'Photo Gallery', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '', '', '', 'Photo Gallery', 'Termag', 'galerija', 5, 'en', '', '', ''),
(61, 'Jahorina in Winter – Olympic Beauty', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Sports and Olympic Centre Jahorina is situated on Jahorina Mountain. In 1984, Sarajevo and Jahorina Mountain hosted the 14th Winter Olympics and the mountain remains one of the largest skiing and winter tourism centres in the Balkans. The highest mountain peak is Ogorjelica, 1916m above sea level, followed by Sjendiste (1910m), Kosuta (1907m) and Crni vrh (1788m). During the winter season the mountain is often covered with as much as three metres of snow cover for 170 days a year on average.<br /><br />Over 20km of excellent ski slopes and 9 ski lifts which can transport over 10,000 skiers in an hour welcome you at your arrival.<br /><br />The mountain is covered with snow for 175 days a year on average, from October to end of May. Average snow cover height in a ten-year period is 106cm. This is due to the fact that the mountain is located in the crossroads of Mediterranean and continental air masses ensuring specific and pleasant climate all year round. <br /><br /><br /> <a class="link_plavi" href="javascript:mapaSkiStaza()" target="_top">View map of Jahorina ski slopes&gt;</a></p>', 'jahorina_zimi_gore.jpg', 'jahorina_zimi_lijevo.jpg', 'Jahorina in Winter ', 'Termag', 'jahorina_zimi', 2, 'en', '', '', ''),
(62, 'Jahorina in Summer – magnificent nature', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>In summer, the mountain is covered with green grass fields, trees &ndash; beech, fir, spruce &ndash; spacious meadows and pastures. The climate is pleasant and mild with wonderful spring and summer offering excellent conditions for various sports trainings, guests with respiratory tract diseases, such as asthma, as well as for all those who are willing to explore and enjoy the magic of this mountain beauty. It is no wonder Jahoina Mountain is declared a national park. Hiking through meadows and mountain fields abounding in blueberries, cranberries, wild strawberries and mushrooms enables you to enjoy these untouched products of nature and intoxicating smell of herbs. <br /><br />Termag Hotel offers wide selection of outdoor summer activities to its guests &ndash; hiking, mountaineering, mountain biking, alpinism, paragliding, picnicking, bike riding, quad-biking, hunting, picking of wild berries and herbs, touring of mountain springs, etc.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><a href="extreme_vikend"><span class="link_crveni"><span class="link_crveni">View our Extreme Weekend offer &gt;</span></span></a></p>', 'jahorina_ljeti_gore.jpg', 'jahorina_ljeti_lijevo.jpg', 'Jahorina in Summer ', 'Termag', 'jahorina_ljeti', 3, 'en', '', '', ''),
(63, 'Rooms', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Termag Hotel offers its guests 18 comfortable rooms and 13 suits equipped with modern comforts such as mini bar, phone, Internet and satellite TV. All hotel premises are air conditioned.<br /><br /><strong>Termag A Room</strong> &ndash; classically equipped room with double bed for two. The Hotel has three rooms of this type.<br /><a href="virtual_tour?tip=Soba%20A"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual Tour &gt;</span></a><br /><br /><strong>Termag B Room</strong> &ndash; sleeps two, with single beds. An additional single bed can be arranged upon request. The Hotel has four rooms of this type.<br /><a class="link_crveni" href="virtual_tour?tip=Soba%20B">Virtual Tour  &gt;</a><br /><br /><strong>Termag C Room </strong> &ndash; sleeps two, with a double bed. An additional single bed can be arranged upon request. The Hotel has three rooms of this type. <br /><a class="link_crveni" href="virtual_tour?tip=Soba%20C">Virtual Tour  &gt;</a><br /><br /><strong>Termag D Room </strong> &ndash; sleeps three persons, with one double bed and one single bed. Additional single bed can be arranged upon request. The Hotel has two rooms of this type. <br /><a href="virtual_tour?tip=Soba%20D"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual Tour  &gt;</span></a><br /><br /><strong>Termag E Room </strong> - twin room with luxurious ensuite bathroom. Additional single bed can be arranged upon request. The Hotel has two rooms of this type. <br /><a href="virtual_tour?tip=Soba%20E"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual Tour  &gt;</span></a><br /><br />All rooms are decorated in a neo-country style and exude rustic atmosphere. Each room has a phone, high-speed Internet connection, cable TV with local and satellite channels, safe, mini bar and 24-hour available room-service. Each room also has an underground parking place reserved for the occupant guest.<br /><br /><a class="link_crveni" href="galerija/smjestaj">View Photo Gallery&gt;</a><br /><br /></p>', 'sobe-gore.jpg', 'sobe-lijevo.jpg', 'Rooms', 'Smjestaj', 'sobe', 1, 'en', '', '', ''),
(64, 'Suites', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p><strong>Termag Suite A</strong><br />Two bedrooms with double beds. A convertible sofa sleeping two in the living room. Maximum room capacity – six persons. The apartment has two ensuite bathrooms. \r\nThe Hotel has one suite of this type. \r\n<br /><a href="virtual_tour?tip=App%20A"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual Tour &gt;</span></a><br /><br /><strong>Termag Suite B</strong><br />Studio apartment with a double bed. Additional sleeping space for three (one single bed and a convertible sofa sleeping two) can be arranged upon request.\r\nThe Hotel has three suites of this type.\r\n<br /><a href="virtual_tour?tip=App%20B"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual Tour &gt;</span></a><br /><br /><strong>Termag Suite C</strong><br />Two-bedroom suite with one double bed and one single bed.  Two additional single beds can be arranged upon request.\r\nThe Hotel has two suites of this type.\r\n<br /><a class="link_crveni" href="virtual_tour?tip=App%20C">Virtual Tour &gt;</a><br /><br /><strong>Termag Suite D</strong><br />One-bedroom suite with double bed and a convertible sofa sleeping two in the living room. \r\nThe Hotel has two suites of this type.\r\n<br /><a class="link_crveni" href="virtual_tour?tip=App%20D">Virtual Tour&gt;</a><br /><br /><strong>Termag Suite E </strong><br />Studio apartment with double bed.  Two additional single beds can be arranged upon request. \r\nThe Hotel has two suites of this type. \r\n<br /><a class="link_crveni" href="virtual_tour?tip=App%20E">Virtual Tour &gt;</a><br /><br /><a href="galerija/smjestaj"><span class="link_crveni">View Photo Gallery&gt;</span></a></p>', 'apartmani-gore.jpg', 'apartmani-lijevo.jpg', 'Suites', 'Smjestaj', 'apartmani', 2, 'en', '', '', ''),
(65, 'Termag Villa', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Termag Villa is a separate apartment building with four apartments located just 200m from Termag Hotel.  All apartments have a fireplace, a LED TV, a DVD, Wi-Fi Internet connection and phone.<br /><br /><strong>Termag Villa Apartment A</strong><br />The apartment consists of a kitchen, a living room, a bedroom and a bathroom. The bedroom has a double bed, while three additional single beds can be arranged in the living room upon request. Termag Villa has two apartments of this type.<br /><a href="virtual_tour?tip=Villa%20A"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual Tour &gt;</span></a><br /><br /><strong>Termag Villa Apartment B </strong><br />This duplex apartment sleeps eight and consists of a living room and a bedroom sleeping two on the first level, and two bedrooms sleeping three (one double bed and one single bed ) on the second level. Additional single bed in the living room can be arranged upon request. Termag Villa has two apartments of this type.<br /><a href="virtual_tour?tip=Villa%20B"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual Tour &gt;</span></a><br /><br /><a class="link_crveni" href="galerija/smjestaj">View Photo Gallery&gt;</a></p>', 'villa-termag-gore.jpg', 'villa-termag-lijevo.jpg', 'Termag Villa', 'Smjestaj', 'villa_termag', 3, 'en', '', '', ''),
(66, 'How to find us ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Termag Hotel is located on Olympic mountain Jahorina, which is well connected to all major cities in Bosnia and Herzegovina and the region. Sarajevo is the closest city, from which the mountain can be reached via Pale (28km) and via Trebevic Mountain (32km). Jahorina Mountain is located 270km from Banja Luka, 320km from Belgrade and 385km from Zagreb.<br /><br />An international airport is located in each of these cities. Sarajevo International Airport is located 30km from Jahorina Mountain. Transfer time by car lasts about 30 minutes. Taxi service between the Airport and our Hotel is also available all year round.<br /><br />Regular bus lines from Sarajevo, Banja Luka, Brcko, Belgrade and other cities to Jahorina Mountain are also available during the whole year. In winter season, large number of tourist agencies organize bus or minibus transfer (on Saturdays) to Jahorina Mountain.<br /><br />Access and distance from major cities in Bosnia and Herzegovina and the region:<br /><br /></p>\r\n<table style="height: 80px; width: 100%;" border="0" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Sarajevo (Pale) 28km</td>\r\n<td>Sarajevo (Trebevic) 32km</td>\r\n<td>Zagreb 385km</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Belgrade 315km</td>\r\n<td>Banja Luka 270km</td>\r\n<td>Brcko 294km</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Novi Sad 322km</td>\r\n<td>Podgorica 268km</td>\r\n<td>Ljubljana 522km</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><a class="link_plavi" href="javascript:lokacijaHotela()" target="_top">View map &gt;</a></p>', 'lokacija_gore.jpg', 'lokacija_lijevo.jpg', 'Location ', 'Termag', 'lokacija', 4, 'en', '', '', ''),
(67, 'Your personal oasis – for your special day ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Our Hotel&rsquo;s guests can enjoy a wide variety of services including swimming pool, Jacuzzi, sauna, steam bath, fitness centre, solarium and SPA&amp;Wellness Centre.<br /><br />Top quality finish and materials have been used in construction of our SPA&amp;Wellness Centre, swimming pool and fitness centre, which together with state-of-the-art equipment and devices, guarantee complete relaxation for our guests. Our professional therapists will help you choose the massage or treatment, from the wide selection we offer, which will best soothe your needs.<br /><br />The Spa&amp;Wellness Centre provides all guest users with towels, bathrobes, slippers and a personal locker during their treatment.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Swimming pool water in our Hotel contains ozone. Manifold beneficial effects of the ozone for the skin and whole body are well known: <br />* It destroys bacteria, viruses and fungus<br />** It improves the level of body oxygen supply<br />*** It speeds up the process of disintegration of unhealthy substances<br />**** It rejuvenates the skin<br /><br /><a href="virtual_tour_dodatno?tip=Wellness"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual Tour &gt;</span></a><br /><br /><a class="link_crveni" href="galerija/spa">View Photo Gallery&gt;</a></p>', 'spa-gore.jpg', 'spa-lijevo.jpg', 'Spa&Welness Centre', 'Spa&Welness', 'spa_centar', 1, 'en', '', '', ''),
(68, 'Massages and Treatments', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'autor', '<p><strong></strong><strong>THAI massage</strong> &ndash; &ndash; In the Far East it is believed that stress, busy everyday lifestyle and fatigue cause misbalance of energy flow in the body, loss of positive energy and piling up of negative energy. This results in feeling tired, lifeless or tense, we may suffer insomnia and backache. Thai massage we offer is based on this holistic principle relieving you from stress and fatigue consequences and renewing your energy and vitality.<br /><br /><strong>Sports massage </strong> &ndash; Serves as preparation for sports activities. The massage is performed just before trainings or other sports activities aiming at preparing your body for the upcoming physical effort. <br /><br /><strong>Classic massage </strong> &ndash; This is a classic body massage with soothing essential oils helping you to relax and enjoy your vacation.<br /><br /><strong>Foot massage </strong> &ndash; This is a massage technique that has been used in China for centuries. A detailed, gentle foot massage stimulates points of vital functions located on your feet making you feel relaxed and calm.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Detox program</strong> &ndash; Program for releasing the toxins from skin making it firm and purified. The treatment induces metabolic processes in skin cells aiding natural defence mechanisms of the skin.</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Health program &ndash; Herbal Beauty&ndash;</strong> The programadjusted to your specific needs. Carefully selected herbs are hand-picked on the slopes of Jahorina Mountain. Warm herbal pillows are used for a relaxing, detoxicating massage inciting better blood flow.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Smell of Sea &ndash; Algae Treatmen</strong>t &ndash; Recommended even for pregnant women.Natural sea salt combined with algae is intended for purifying, hydration and firming of the skin.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Do you like chocolate?</strong>!&ndash; Open your mind to the sensational feeling of chocolate on your skin... Treatment with pure warm chocolate brings back the balance in the energy flow while decreasing tension and stress. The smell of chocolate stimulates serotonin &ndash; &ldquo;the hormone of happiness&rdquo;. The minerals nurture the skin, which results in soft, silk-like skin.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Brazilian Treatment</strong>&ndash;Brazilian energy and refreshing tropical rain alternate during this treatment while your senses are intoxicated by the smells of coconuts, lime... The treatment nurtures the skin, incites blood flow and relaxes.&nbsp;</p>', 'spa-masaze-gore.jpg', 'spa-masaze-lijevo.jpg', 'Massages and Treatments', 'Spa&welness', 'masaze_i_tretmani', 2, 'en', '', '', ''),
(69, 'Daily SPA', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>You can enjoy wide selection of treatments, massages and other services of our Spa&amp;Wellness Centre even if you are not staying in our Hotel.<br /><br />Visit us when it suits you best, everyday from 10.00a.m. to 10.00p.m.. Become a Member of Termag Spa&amp;Wellness Club and enjoy the benefits of additional services and discounts. Calls and we will help you design your personal Spa&amp;Wellness programme!<br /><br />Therapeutic effect of water combined with massage improves overall health relieving you from stress and fatigue. Relaxation in swimming pool, steam bath, sauna, Jacuzzi, or massage eases everyday pressure and helps in maintaining health by relieving you from dangers and risks caused by everyday exposure to stress. Visit our Spa&amp;Wellness Centre and make sure yourself!</p>', 'daily-spa-gore.jpg', 'daily-spa-lijevo.jpg', 'Special Offers', 'Spa&welness', 'vanpensionska_ponuda', 3, 'en', '', '', ''),
(70, 'Hotel Restaurant ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Hotel&rsquo;s Grand Restaurant offers our guests a wide variety of international and local cuisine. Our specialties are traditional Bosnian sweets and cakes. Grand Restaurant is a self-service restaurant and can serve up to 120 guests.<br /><br />Its carefully designed interior and pleasant welcoming atmosphere will make you smile and will forever remain your dearest memory. Our professional staff and top chiefs ensure highest quality service, while a wide selection of wines will satisfy the best connoisseurs.<br /><br />Breakfast: 08:00 - 11:00 h<br /><br />Dinner: 18:00 &ndash; 21:00 h<br /><br /><a href="virtual_tour_dodatno?tip=Restoran"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual Tour &gt;</span></a></p>', 'hotelski_restoran_gore.jpg', 'hotelski_restoran_lijevo.jpg', 'Hotel Restaurant ', 'Restorani', 'hotelski_restoran', 1, 'en', '', '', ''),
(71, 'Kamin Sala', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Warmth and crackling of the fireplace in Kamin sala create a rustic atmosphere for your relaxation. The Restaurant offers a wide variety of specialities of international and local cuisine and a wide selection of carefully selected local and imported wines. Kamin sala has a unique and exclusive interior dominated by natural materials with a magnificent view of the ski slopes and forests of Jahorina Ski Centre.<br /><br />Restaurant Working Hours: 09:00a.m. &ndash; 12:00a.m. <br /><br /> <a class="link_crveni" href="galerija/restorani">View Photo Gallery&gt;</a></p>', 'kamin_sala_gore.jpg', 'kamin_sala_lijevo.jpg', 'Kamin sala', 'Restorani', 'kamin_sala', 2, 'en', '', '', ''),
(72, 'Koliba – The best fun in the mountain! ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>In close proximity of the Hotel, next to the ski slope, following the sound of the mountain spring, you will reach Termag ethno restaurant Koliba. The Restaurant terrace blends in with the natural surroundings offering an excellent place for relaxing while feeling in harmony with nature. The Restaurant offers a wide selection menu and high-quality cuisine for you to enjoy after long walks, or in the evenings, after a long day of skiing or enjoying other mountain activities. Cosy, home-like atmosphere of the Restaurant is created by a meticulously designed interior dominated by wood and carefully chosen details intended to enrich the feeling of warmth and pleasant ambient.<br /><br />During the winter season, theme apr&egrave;s ski parties lasting until dawn are organized, enabling you to enjoy clubbing atmosphere and excellent music. <br /><br /> <a href="virtual_tour_dodatno?tip=Koliba"><span class="link_crveni">Virtual Tour &gt;</span></a><br /><br /> <a class="link_crveni" href="galerija/koliba">View Photo Gallery&gt;</a></p>', 'koliba_gore.jpg', 'koliba_lijevo.jpg', 'Koliba', 'Restorani', 'koliba', 3, 'en', '', '', ''),
(73, 'Family Weekend ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<div class="centriran_tekst">\r\n<ul class="bullet_zeleni obojena_lista">\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Two nights, Friday to Sunday, half-board (dinner and breakfast)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free stay for children under 10.</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of swimming pool, sauna and steam bath</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>2x aroma therapy oils massage (40min)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Bathrobe and slippers during your stay.</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>A box of chocolates for a warm welcome</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Late Sunday check-out (16h)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>The price includes full package (two adults and two children under 10)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="ponude_cijena">FULL PACKAGE Suite 500BAM (256EUR)</p>\r\n<p>SPRING | SUMMER PACKAGES</p>\r\n<p>Packages are offered on weekends, from April to December.</p>\r\n<p>The prices are per person, for a complete package. If you reserve a double bed or a twin room for one person, additional 50BAM are charged.</p>\r\n</div>', 'porodicni_gore.jpg', 'porodicni_lijevo.jpg', 'Family Weekend', 'Specijalne ponude', 'porodicni_vikend', 1, 'en', '', '', ''),
(74, 'Relax Weekend', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<div class="centriran_tekst">\r\n<ul class="bullet_narandzasti obojena_lista">\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Two nights, Friday to Sunday, half-board (dinner and breakfast)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of swimming pool, sauna and steam bath</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>2x relaxing aroma therapy oils massage (40min)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of bicycle throughout weekend</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Bathrobe and slippers during your stay.</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>A box of chocolates for a warm welcome</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Late Sunday check-out (16h).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="ponude_cijena">Room 230BAM (118 EUR) | Suite 255BAM (131 EUR)</p>\r\n<p>SPRING | SUMMER PACKAGES</p>\r\n<p>Packages are offered on weekends, from April to December.</p>\r\n<p>The prices are per person, for a complete package. If you reserve a double bed or a twin room for one person, additional 50BAM are charged.</p>\r\n</div>', 'relax_gore.jpg', 'relax_lijevo.jpg', 'Relax Weekend ', 'Specijalne ponude', 'relax_vikend', 2, 'en', '', '', ''),
(75, 'Romance Weekend', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<div class="centriran_tekst">\r\n<ul class="bullet_crveni obojena_lista">\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Two nights, Friday to Sunday, half-board (dinner and breakfast)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of swimming pool, sauna and steam bath</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x romantic dinner with candle lights and champagne</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x breakfast in bed</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x relaxing aroma therapy oils massage (40min)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x relaxing bath (Babor Cosmetics), 20-30min (relaxes, relieves stress, nurtures skin, leaves delicate scent)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of bicycle throughout weekend.</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Bathrobe and slippers during your stay</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>A box of chocolates for a warm welcome</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Late Sunday check-out (16h).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="ponude_cijena">Room 230BAM (118EUR) | Suite 255BAM (131EUR)</p>\r\n<p>SPRING | SUMMER PACKAGES</p>\r\n<p>Packages are offered on weekends, from April to December.</p>\r\n<p>The prices are per person, for a complete package. If you reserve a double bed or a twin room for one person, additional 50BAM are charged.</p>\r\n</div>', 'romanticni_gore.jpg', 'romanticni_lijevo.jpg', 'Romance Weekend', 'Specijalne ponude', 'romanticni_vikend', 3, 'en', '', '', ''),
(76, 'Anti-stress Weekend ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'autor', '<div class="centriran_tekst">\r\n<ul class="bullet_tamno_plavi obojena_lista">\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Two nights, Friday to Sunday, half-board (dinner and breakfast)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of swimming pool, sauna and steam bath</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x Thai massage with crystals (traditional Thai massage targeting energy balance, reliving negative energy, helping immune system)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x ScenTao bath (Babor Cosmetics), 20-30min (relaxing exotic experience for all senses, softens and nurtures skin)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x herbal foot bath (Babor Cosmetics), 30min (refreshing and purifying, prevents sweating)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x foot massage (30min)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of bicycle throughout weekend</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Bathrobe and slippers during your stay</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>A box of chocolates for a warm welcome</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Late Sunday check-out (16h)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="ponude_cijena">Room 295BAM (151EUR) | Suite 320BAM (164EUR)</p>\r\n<p>SPRING | SUMMER PACKAGES</p>\r\n<p>Packages are offered on weekends, from April to December.</p>\r\n<p>The prices are per person, for a complete package. If you reserve a double bed or a twin room for one person, additional 50BAM are charged.</p>\r\n</div>', 'antistress_gore.jpg', 'antistress_lijevo.jpg', 'Anti-stress Weekend ', 'Specijalne ponude', 'antistress_vikend', 4, 'en', '', '', ''),
(77, 'Extreme Weekend', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<div class="centriran_tekst">\r\n<ul class="bullet_svijetlo_narandzasti obojena_lista">\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Two nights, Friday to Sunday, half-board (dinner and breakfast)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of swimming pool, sauna and steam bath</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x tandem paragliding with experienced instructor (depending on weather conditions), transportation to take off spot on Gola Jahorina and return from landing spot in Vrhprača, CD with photos</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x adrenaline ride (1h) on quad bike (experience off road ride with a lot of fun and excitement)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>1x relaxing bath (Babor Cosmetics), 20-30min (relaxes, relieves stress, nurtures skin, leaves delicate scent)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of bicycle throughout weekend</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Bathrobe and slippers during your stay</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>A box of chocolates for a warm welcome</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Late Sunday check-out (16h)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="ponude_cijena">Room 1/2 330BAM (169EUR) | Suite 1/2 355BAM (182EUR)</p>\r\n<p>SPRING | SUMMER PACKAGES</p>\r\n<p>Packages are offered on weekends, from April to December.</p>\r\n<p>The prices are per person, for a complete package. If you reserve a double bed or a twin room for one person, additional 50BAM are charged.</p>\r\n</div>', 'extreme_gore.jpg', 'extreme_lijevo.jpg', 'Extreme Weekend', 'Specijalne ponude', 'extreme_vikend', 5, 'en', '', '', ''),
(78, 'Life is Play ...', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<div class="centriran_tekst">\r\n<ul class="bullet_svijetlo_plavi obojena_lista">\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Two nights, Friday to Sunday, half-board (dinner and breakfast)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of swimming pool, sauna and steam bath</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>2x relaxing aroma therapy oils massage (40min)</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Free use of bicycle throughout the weekend</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Transport to Coloseum Club in Sarajevo and return to the Hotel</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Welcome drink and free entrance to Casino and Club</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Bathrobe and slippers during your stay</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>A box of chocolates for a warm welcome</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;</span>Late Sunday check-out (16h)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="ponude_cijena">Room 1/2 235BAM (120.50EUR) | Suite 1/2 260BAM (133EUR)</p>\r\n<p>SPRING | SUMMER PACKAGES</p>\r\n<p>Packages are offered on weekends, from April to December.</p>\r\n<p>The prices are per person, for a complete package. If you reserve a double bed or a twin room for one person, additional 50BAM are charged.</p>\r\n</div>', 'casino_gore.jpg', 'casino_lijevo.jpg', 'Life is Play ...', 'Specijalne ponude', 'zivot_je_igra', 6, 'en', '', '', ''),
(79, 'Breaking bread breaks barrieras', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Termag Hotel is recognized as an ideal place for holding business meetings, trainings or seminars, conferences and team buildings. Weather you are taking your client for dinner or just having dinner with friends, our staff will provide you with the most appropriate services as well as enable privacy for conducting business. An incredibly comfortable and functional seminar and conference room can host between 30 and 70 people, depending on the sitting arrangement. Translator boots and translation equipment can be arranged upon request. <br /><br /><a class="link_crveni" href="rezervacije">Make an Appointment&gt;</a></p>', 'business-ponuda-gore.jpg', 'business-ponuda-lijevo.jpg', 'Offers ', 'Business', 'ponuda', 2, 'en', '', '', ''),
(80, 'Contact information ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>For all information, reservations and special requests, contacts us at: <br />Information and reservations:<br />Hotel Termag Jahorina<br />Poljice bb, Bosna i Hercegovina<br />Phone: +387 57 270 422, +387 57 272 100<br />Fax: +387 57 270 423, +387 57 272 072<br />E-mail: termag@teol.net <br />GPS:<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Latitude: 43.735296<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Longitude: 18.567819<br /><br /> <a class="link_crveni" href="kontakt_forma"><span class="link_crveni">Send your request online&gt;</span></a></p>', 'kontakt_info_gore.jpg', 'kontakt_info_lijevo.jpg', 'Contact us', 'meni-gore', 'kontaktirajte_nas', 0, 'en', '', '', ''),
(81, 'Weather Forecast ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Warm Mediterranean and cold continental air masses meet on Jahorina Mountain making it a natural beauty with a favourable and healthy climate, and temperatures to ensure a pleasant stay in both winter and summer. The climate on Jahorina also guarantees large amounts of snow in winter with an average of 85 days of snowfall a year. On average, the mountain is covered with snow for 175 days between October and the end of May. This makes Jahorina a unique mountain in the region. The thickness of snow cover ranges between one and three meters, while the average thickness of snow cover from October to May is 106cm. Jahorina snow is of highest quality for skiing and other winter sports.<br /><br />In the spring, when the snow melts and skiers leave the mountain, vegetation starts to bloom and Jahorina offers new experiences and numerous opportunities for hikers, alpinists, speleologists, hunters and fishermen. It also offers great conditions and is suitable for altitude training. Those who enjoy nature will find peace and a true vacation here. Mountain springs, enormous green spaces, intoxicating air &ndash; all work to the benefit of your vacation <br /><br /></p>', 'vrijeme_gore.jpg', 'vrijeme_lijevo.jpg', 'Weather Forecast ', 'meni-gore', 'vrijeme', 0, 'en', '', '', ''),
(82, 'Gift Card ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>If you are looking for a special luxury gift, we offer you our Gift Card for a stay in our Hotel, dinner in one of our Restaurants or for use of the service in our Spa&Wellness Centre. Order your Gift Card online by filling in the form below. </p>', 'poklon_vaucer_gore.jpg', 'poklon_vaucer_lijevo.jpg', 'Gift Card ', 'Specijalne ponude', 'poklon_vaucer', 7, 'en', '', '', ''),
(83, 'Online request form', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Contact Termag Hotel, tell us your business event requests and we will organize it to you complete satisfaction. If you would like to visit Termag Hotel as a group, please fill in the form below and you will be contacted by our Hotel&rsquo;s managers as soon as possible.</p>', 'business-upit-gore.jpg', 'business-upit-lijevo.jpg', 'Reservations ', 'Business', 'rezervacije', 4, 'en', '', '', ''),
(84, 'Seminars', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Hotel Termag is well known as an ideal place to hold business meetings, trainings, conferences and team building activities and retreats. Whether you are taking a client for a dinner, celebrating business success or just having a dinner with your friends our staff will provide excellent service, as well as privacy. A surprisingly pleasant and functional space is dedicated for holding smaller seminars and conferences. It can accommodate from 30 to 70 participants, depending on the room configuration. Space is fit for installment of translation equipment.</p>\r\n<p><a class="link_crveni" href="rezervacije">Schedule a meeting&gt;</a></p>', 'business-seminari-gore.jpg', 'business-seminari-lijevo.jpg', 'Seminars', 'Business', 'seminari', 1, 'en', '', '', ''),
(85, 'Team Building', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Our team-building programs are implemented by a group of certified and experienced trainers. The offered programs include various creative activities in open and closed space and are available during all seasons. At the heart of every team building program is team development, as well as development of communication and motivation, leading to creative problem solving.</p>\r\n<p><br /><br />The concept behind our team-building programs includes finding solutions in the new surroundings, far away from the work place. In other words, it is a series of strategic games that your employees have to solve while competing with their peers.</p>\r\n<p><br /><br />A content of your team-building program is defined in accordance with your needs and goals, so please be so kind and <a class="link_crveni" href="rezervacije">email us</a> your basic info and goals, and you will receive a personalized offer in no time.<br /><br /></p>', 'business-team-gore.jpg', 'business-team-lijevo.jpg', 'Team Building', 'Business', 'team_building', 3, 'en', '', '', ''),
