(89, 'Children’s Corner', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '<p>Play Room is dedicated for our youngest guests&ndash; a large space with toys, pool tables and two Play Stations, guarantees that your children will be happy and will let you catch a couple of hours just for yourself.<br /><br /> Play Room working hours are 9.00 - 22.00, with a break between 18.00 -19.30. The period between 19.30 -22.00 is reserved for specially organized workshops and games for children with experienced staff.<br /><br /> <span style="color: #ff0000;">THEME EVENINGS ORGANIZED BY PROFESSIONAL TEAMS</span><br /> Music evening, sports evening, snow games, quizzes, costume parties&hellip; Variety of offers to suit variety of your interests. We can also arrange babysitting for a child under three or taking care of your child during the night.<br /><br /> Our professional staff will provide highest level of care for our youngest guests and allow the parents to fully enjoy their time at our Hotel.</p>', 'igraonica-gore.jpg', 'igraonica-lijevo.jpg', 'Children’s Corner', 'Smjestaj', 'igraonica', 7, 'en', '', '', ''),
